data.title: Holy Family Catholic Academy
data.text:
Holy Family Catholic Academy is a parochial and private school for students in preschool through 8th grade.

Holy Family Preschool serves students from age 2 years 10 months.

Our educated and professional teachers love working with and for the children and their families.

The faculty, staff, students and their families at Holy Family Catholic Academy appreciate you and welcome your partnership and support!
